Package hu.elte.txtuml.stdlib

Contains the txtUML standard library which consists of external classes (subclasses of ExternalClass) that might be used to enhance the model with some special features which are not part of the standard UML2, like Timers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Timer
    An external class which enhances the txtUML models with the ability of using timed events.
    Timer.Handle
    The handle of a certain timed event created by the Timer class.

Package hu.elte.txtuml.stdlib Description

Contains the txtUML standard library which consists of external classes (subclasses of ExternalClass) that might be used to enhance the model with some special features which are not part of the standard UML2, like Timers.
